data.description:
CoroWatch Inspired from foobacca's very fuzzy time, and mod to Java Translated, this text is under development stage.
PBW Khusus wong jowo wae..

Jam iki ora kok pitu lebih limo, tapi pitu limo.
7:00 = pitu pas..
7:05 = pitu limo
7:11 = pitu swelas
7:12 = pitu rolas
7:35 = pitu telu limo
